\n有錯就左賴右賴 人地出錯instruction<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5de6874a3b43ca02b799cc55fbc76769791b34a","tid":481980,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:14:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無人發覺qr code 根本就係為左比用低階機既人 可以參與mobile payment<br />\n<br />\n低階機無fingerprint 無nfc (雖然而家大部分有)<br />\n所以咪要開個相機用qr code<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係大陸好多人都係用垃圾機<br />\n所以佢梗係要整個人人都用到既方法</blockquote><br />\n好多大陸狗黎香港買野 影qr code<br />\n部垃圾機 開鏡頭對焦都搞幾秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不點名批評OPPO"},{"pid":"f64accf8b5e25b99fb2bd29e3521c1b6ff193f43","tid":481980,"uid":131430,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:14:30.000Z","msg":"你拎20 年前科技出黎講<br />\n咁barcode 絕左種未呀"},{"pid":"dd6190c2e6dd7cbb8bbac2b5f8a0d9acdd51cc23","tid":481980,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你拎20 年前科技出黎講<br />\n咁barcode 絕左種未呀</blockquote><br />\n你又係做倉架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7269d21ec71adb1896fb6b21f93c11640a87b5fb","tid":481980,"uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:17:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用NFC <br />\n開機wallet<br />\n指紋摸一摸 <br />\n放近部機<br />\n就完<br />\n<br />\n成件事型到爆<br />\n<br />\nQR Code 方式<br />\n攞部機開鏡頭 <br />\n對準QR Code<br />\nSet 入幾錢<br />\n入PIN <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點忍受自己做咁柒既事呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下用黎做咩啦 如果你話係搭火車緊係nfc方便<br />\n<br />\n但係街邊d廣告 上網見到d優惠之類 唯有係qr code"},{"pid":"d4a31c1b31165bfb20062f738045dff7428448db","tid":481980,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"rep