ormal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點忍受自己做咁柒既事呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下用黎做咩啦 如果你話係搭火車緊係nfc方便<br />\n<br />\n但係街邊d廣告 上網見到d優惠之類 唯有係qr code</blockquote><br />\n唯有係優惠 或者部分printed ads上既qr code<br />\n有好多qr code 都係印係impractical既位<br />\n例如車身車尾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外國都有人寫文話用qr code 對於提升audience數量都幫唔上忙</blockquote><br />\n補充番<br />\n而家反而用得最好既地方係food labeling/睇GM FOOD/Ingredients</blockquote><br />\n其實依兩樣野無衝突 樓主個比較其實係唔成立  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df80815d825359acc4c5a4642924327a0d37190","tid":481980,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:31:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用NFC <br />\n開機wallet<br />\n指紋摸一摸 <br />\n放近部機<br />\n就完<br />\n<br />\n成件事型到爆<br />\n<br />\nQR Code 方式<br />\n攞部機開鏡頭 <br />\n對準QR Code<br />\nSet 入幾錢<br />\n入PIN <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點忍受自己做咁柒既事呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇下用黎做咩啦 如果你話係搭火車緊係nfc方便<br />\n<br />\n但係街邊d廣告 上網見到d優惠之類 唯有係qr code</blockquote><br />\n唯有係優惠 或者部分printed ads上既qr code<br />\n有好多qr code 都係印係impractical既位<br />\n例如車身車尾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外國都有人寫文話用qr code 對於提升audience數量都幫唔上忙</blockquote><br />\n補充番<br />\n而家反而用得最好既地方係food labeling/睇GM FOOD/Ingredients</blockquote><br />\n其實依兩樣野無衝突 樓主個比較其實係唔成立  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊mobile payment<br />\n唔係點會講qr code set入幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8cc24c07f0fc985b4f7e97cc42db080a1d4f0f","tid":481980,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:34:04.000Z","msg":"唔係話幫支那style，但qr code payment真係做到0成本（對買賣假方都係）<br />\n如果nfc有朝一日唔洗每個交易都比人袋幾%，我諗9成人會即轉"},{"pid":"7e6d9